            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "what we would need is some textual representation that directly maps to any missing element of the tree-sitter grammar. So we can have a buffer with somehing like `x = funccal(a, b + {expr-hole}, c);` where `{expr-hole}` is an unambiguous representation of a missing expression node.",
